 be included here, they have taken a big step towards the rectification of identities for many leading personalities. In so doing, he has done us all a great service.” - Professor Wang Gungwu, National University of Singapore  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aChinesezSoutheast AsiavBiographyvDictionaries. 0aChinese--Southeast Asia--Biography--Dictionaries. 0aChinese--Southeast Asia--Biography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aSuryadinata, Leo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt40uhttps://doi.org/10.1355/978981441414240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789814414142423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789814414142.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles